videos.description: Southeast Missouri State gets out on the fast break finishing with Isiah Jones throwing up the high lob to Antonius Cleveland for the powerful dunk.
videos.headline: Sky-high alley-oop for SE Missouri State

videos.description: 1H (14:14) MURR Damarcus Croaker made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Gee McGhee.

videos.description: 1H (9:26) SEMO Eric McGill with another Three Point Jumper. The home crowd is lovin it.
